ground:#fafafc;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;height:100%;margin:0;padding:0;width:100%"><table class="main-wrapper" width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#fafafc;margin:0;padding:0;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;height:100%;line-height:100%;width:100%"><tr><td class="main-wrapper__inner" align="left" valign="top" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-bottom:40px;padding-top:40px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><div class="newsletter" style="background:url(/media/newsletter/issues/no17/background.png) center 100px repeat-y #fff;margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px"><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-6 is-first py-1" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:300px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding-bottom:10px;padding-top:10px" align="left"><img src="/media/newsletter/issues/no17/logo.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none"/></td><td class="column-6 has-text-right is-last py-1" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;padding-left:10px;width:300px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:right;padding-bottom:10px;padding-top:10px" align="right"><span class="newsletter__issue-number" style="color:#3b3081;font-weight:bolder">Issue #17 - May 2022</span></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-12 is-first is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;width:600px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;line-height:1.25;margin:60px auto;text-align:center">Hi! <strong style="display:block;font-size:30px;font-weight:bolder">Do you like our content?</strong> </span><img class="newsletter__img__intro" src="/media/newsletter/issues/no17/img-intro.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none;display:block;margin:0 auto 60px"/><div class="newsletter__text is-large" style="color:#6b6b70;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px"><p>We accumulated a vast amount of experience and knowledge about product development during our projects and had the opportunity to peek behind the scenes of dozens of startups. During the past year or so, we wrote, filmed and recorded hours of content where we shared this knowledge.</p><p>If you like our content, you can help us. We would like to share this wisdom with even more people. Be it a guest post, video, podcast or even as a speaker, as we did at the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S_wBoJgpnyo" target="_blank" style="color:#3b3081;text-decoration:none">Founders Festival</a>.</p><p>We didn't advertise this yet. But now, since you know, don't hold back if you know someone who would find our content interesting.</p><table class="button is-rounded mx-auto" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;padding-bottom:15px;padding-left:35px;padding-right:35px;padding-top:15px;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/contact" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none">I know someone who would be interested in your content »</a></td></tr></table></div></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-7 is-first" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:350px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__section-title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 45px">Blog &raquo;</span> <span class="newsletter__content__tag" style="background-color:#6b6b70;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;color:#fff;display:block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:15px;padding:5px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;width:max-content">Startup</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">How to use the value proposition canvas?</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>Why is your value proposition an important part of your business plan? How to formulate it? How to visualize it using the value proposition canvas? Read on, to find answer to these questions and more.</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/blog/posts/how-to-use-the-value-proposition-canvas?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=17th_issue" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Read on</a></td></tr></table><br/><br/></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-7 is-first" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:350px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__content__tag" style="background-color:#6b6b70;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;color:#fff;display:block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:15px;padding:5px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;width:max-content">Life at Further</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">Further Was Recognized by Clutch as a Leading 2022 B2B Service Provider in Romania</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>We're happy to announce that we've been named as a top provider of B2B services in 2022. According to Clutch, we're among the leading software developers in Romania this year!</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/blog/posts/further-recognized-as-2022-leading-b2b-service-provider?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=17th_issue" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Read on</a></td></tr></table></td><td class="column-5 is-hidden-sm is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;width:250px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><img class="image-pulled-right" src="/media/newsletter/issues/no17/img-blog.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none;float:right;margin-right:-20px"/></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-5 is-hidden-sm is-first" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:250px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><img class="image-pulled-left" src="/media/newsletter/issues/no17/img-events.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none;float:left;margin-left:-20px"/></td><td class="column-7 is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;width:350px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__section-title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 45px">Event recap &raquo;</span> <span class="newsletter__content__tag" style="background-color:#6b6b70;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;color:#fff;display:block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:15px;padding:5px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;width:max-content">May 5th</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">Founders Festival</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>On May 5th, we had the pleasure to speak at the Founders Festival, which took place at the Anglia Ruskin University in London.</p><p>Our presentation followed up on Chris Fox's talk on business modelling, and it's goal was to dive deeper into customer profiling and introduce personas as a tool.</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S_wBoJgpnyo" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Show me the talk</a></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table class="container newsletter__outro" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:600px;background:url(/media/newsletter/issues/no17/img-outro.png) center top no-repeat;color:#3b3081;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 15px;min-height:325px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-12 is-first is-last" valign="center" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;width:600px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><div class="newsletter__outro__text" style="padding-left:50%;padding-top:10%">What do you think of our newsletter? What can we improve? If you have any thoughts or just want to grab a coffee, please <a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/contact?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=15th_issue" target="_blank" style="color:#3b3081;text-decoration:underline">reach out to us</a>!</div></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 